{"id":4624,"date":"2025-01-16T19:18:19","date_gmt":"2025-01-16T19:18:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4624"},"modified":"2025-01-16T19:19:03","modified_gmt":"2025-01-16T19:19:03","slug":"gen-8-activation","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/game-mechanics\/gen-8-activation\/","title":{"rendered":"Activate Gen 8 Encounters"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Pok\u00e9mon Unbound features Pok\u00e9mon from the Galar region, part of the eighth generation of Pok\u00e9mon games. But Pok\u00e9mon from that region won&#8217;t initially spawn in a new game.<\/p>\n<p>Activating Generation 8 encounters requires you to register at least one Pok\u00e9mon from the Galar region in your Pokedex. There are two primary ways to do this:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Acquire any Gen 8 Pok\u00e9mon via trading<\/li>\n<li>Or use <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/extras\/mystery-gift-codes\/\">Mystery Gift<\/a> to acquire a Gen 8 Pok\u00e9mon like Zarude<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2025\/01\/01-pokemon-unbound-receiving-zarude-through-the-mystery-gift.jpg\" alt=\"Receiving Zarude through the Mystery Gift. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Receiving Zarude through the Mystery Gift.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Trading can be done through Unbound Cloud, but it can still be more tedious than the Mystery Gift option. So Mystery Gift is more recommended. <\/p>\n<p>Before you can do Mystery Gifts you must first defeat the Elite Four. Once you do that, you can look at <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/extras\/mystery-gift-codes\/\">our list of Mystery Gift codes<\/a> to give the code at any Pok\u00e9Center.<\/p>\n<p>After the activation, you can randomly encounter available Galar region Pok\u00e9mon in the wild like any other wild Pok\u00e9mon. <\/p>\n<p>Additionally, the DexNav will randomly encounter Gen 8 Pok\u00e9mon when you roam an area while setting the R button to DexNav.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/game-mechanics\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/bedroom-unbound.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/bedroom-unbound.jpg 400w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/bedroom-unbound-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Game Mechanics<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":4625,"parent":2336,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-4624","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/4624","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2336"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4625"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4624"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4624"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}